Name: Average time from SW-AE Assign Reviewers to SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'

Name: Total time from Manuscript Export Succeeded to SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'

Name: Minimum time from SW-Reviewer Agreed to SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'

Name: Average time between SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation and SW-Awaiting EIC Decision
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation' and activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'

Name: Total resolution time of SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation and the end of the case

Name: Minimum resolution time of SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation and the end of the case

Name: Average waiting time to SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation after Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'

Name: Total time it takes SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation to be done after SW-Checklist Completed
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'

Name: Average time for SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation to lead to SW-EIC Major Revision or SW-EIC Minor Revision
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'begin': "activity == 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'", 'end': "activity == 'SW-EIC Major Revision' or activity == 'SW-EIC Minor Revision'", 'aggregation': 'average', 'filter': '', 'group_by': ''}

Name: Total time for all activities leading up to SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation in the most frequent variant
Metric: The sum of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'

Name: Total time from SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion to SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation across all variants
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'

Name: Average time it takes from SW-AE Assign Reviewers to SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation compared to time from SW-AE Assign Reviewers to SW-Reviewer Agreed
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'begin': "activity == 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'", 'end': "activity == 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation' or activity == 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'", 'aggregation': 'average', 'filter': '', 'group_by': ''}

Name: Total time from SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation to SW-Awaiting EIC Decision in the longest process variant
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation' and activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'
